description: The CDL Super Week is just around the corner. We break down all the matches, including OpTic Chicago v Toronto Ultra, Dallas Empire v Los Angeles Thieves, New York Subliners v London Royal Ravens, Florida Mutineers v Paris Legion, Minnesota Rokkr v Seattle Surge. We discuss the potential return of the Call of Duty franchise to the World War 2 era for Sledgehammer's game in 2021!
